---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
import CtaBlock from '../components/CtaBlock.astro';
---

<Base
  surface="dark"
  title="About"
  description="We started Purpose Brands because brilliant food, drink, and wellness brands deserve better than a spreadsheet-driven Amazon agency."
>
  {/* Intro */}
  <Section tone="dark">
    <div class="about-intro">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>We built the agency we wished existed.</h1>
      <div class="about-intro__body">
        <p>
          Every Amazon agency we met was either a massive machine that forgot your
          name after the pitch, or a one-person show making it up as they went.
        </p>
        <p>
          So we built something different. Two people. Senior from day one. Only
          food, drink, and wellness. Only Amazon.
        </p>
        <p>
          We called it Purpose Brands because we wanted to work with people who
          are building something that actually matters. Not just selling units.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  {/* Phoebe */}
  <Section tone="dark">
    <article class="bio">
      <div class="bio__image" aria-hidden="true">
        <span>Phoebe</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bio__body">
        <p class="eyebrow">Founder</p>
        <h2>Phoebe Bocchinelli</h2>
        <p class="bio__lede">
          15 years in consumer brands. Worked with Moët Hennessy, Veuve Clicquot,
          Heineken, and Belvedere Vodka. 6 of those years specifically on Amazon
          across the UK and US.
        </p>
        <p>
          Started Purpose Brands because too many great brands were getting a raw
          deal from agencies that didn't understand their world. Based on the South
          Devon coast. Happiest near the sea. Will always be honest with you, even
          when it's not what you want to hear.
        </p>
        <ul class="bio__trust" aria-label="Brands Phoebe has worked with">
          <li>Moët Hennessy</li>
          <li>Heineken</li>
          <li>Veuve Clicquot</li>
          <li>Belvedere Vodka</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </article>
  </Section>

  {/* Biraj */}
  <Section tone="dark">
    <article class="bio bio--reverse">
      <div class="bio__image" aria-hidden="true">
        <span>Biraj</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bio__body">
        <p class="eyebrow">Co-founder</p>
        <h2>Biraj Parmar</h2>
        <p class="bio__lede">
          Built an Amazon and D2C brand from scratch. Sold it for seven figures
          in 2021. Stayed on as a brand consultant because he couldn't stop
          tinkering.
        </p>
        <p>
          Has been a seller, a brand owner, an internal consultant, and now the
          person helping your brand win. Knows what works because he's done it
          himself — not because he read a playbook.
        </p>
        <ul class="bio__trust" aria-label="Brands Biraj has worked with">
          <li>Heroes Technology</li>
          <li>Sports Laboratory</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </article>
  </Section>

  {/* SAS */}
  <Section tone="dark">
    <div class="sas">
      <p>
        We're a Surfers Against Sewage Ocean Network member. We live on the South
        Devon coast. Protecting our waters isn't a CSR box-tick — it's personal.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  {/* Bottom CTA */}
  <Section tone="dark">
    <CtaBlock />
  </Section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-intro {
    max-width: 56rem;
  }

  .about-intro h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-display-lg);
    max-width: 18ch;
    margin: 2rem 0 3rem;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .about-intro__body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .about-intro__body p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(250, 250, 247, 0.78);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .bio {
    display: grid;
    gap: 3rem;
    padding-top: 4rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline-dark);
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .bio {
      grid-template-columns: 5fr 7fr;
      gap: 5rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .bio--reverse .bio__image {
      order: 2;
    }
  }

  .bio__image {
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    background: rgba(250, 250, 247, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline-dark);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    max-width: 420px;
  }

  .bio__image span {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: rgba(250, 250, 247, 0.35);
  }

  .bio__body h2 {
    margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .bio__lede {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    max-width: 38ch;
  }

  .bio__body > p {
    color: rgba(250, 250, 247, 0.75);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .bio__trust {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 2rem 0 0;
    margin: 2rem 0 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline-dark);
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.625rem 1rem;
  }

  .bio__trust li {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(250, 250, 247, 0.7);
    padding: 0.5rem 0.875rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline-dark);
    border-radius: 999px;
  }

  .sas {
    max-width: 48ch;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline-dark);
  }

  .sas p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(250, 250, 247, 0.75);
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
